/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a panoramic view of a bustling street in Beijing, China. The vantage point is high, providing a bird's eye view of the urban landscape. The street, lined with trees and lampposts, stretches out into the distance, flanked by buildings on both sides. Power lines crisscross above, forming a complex web against the backdrop of the clear blue sky. The sun shines brightly, casting a warm glow over the scene. The image is taken from a low angle, adding a sense of depth and perspective to the view. The colors are vibrant, with the green of the trees contrasting against the blue of the sky and the various hues of the buildings.
